         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Herennios to Satornilus, his brother and lord, many greetings.  Please give to Stichus the slave of Narcissus his little shield and collected from him the two shirts (?) and the incense on which he agreed with me.  There will be loaves on the ninth.  Concerning the food for NN, deliver it at whatever price you wish.  But if a surplus . . .</ab>
